  <conbody>
    <p><ph keyref="product"/> provides a variety of built-in form controls that allow users to
      interact with documents with familiar user interface objects. For customization purposes, <ph
        keyref="product"/> also supports <xref
        href="implementing-custom-form-controls.dita#implementing-custom-form-controls"
          ><ph>custom form controls in Java</ph></xref>.</p>
    <p>To watch our video demonstration in regards to form controls, go to <xref
        href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/demo/Form_Controls.html" format="html" scope="external"/>.</p>
